snippet.title: Amber Heard 'terrible' moments
snippet.description:
five moments in no particular order of awfulness. 1. She appeared on overhaulin, a reality show where she was pranked. 2. Whoa. psycho. 3. The baby she snatched from the nurse was really sick and was too dangerous to carry the baby around. The other child she carried was Kate James (her ex assistant) child. Kate claimed her boy was terrified when she put him in front of the cameras as part of her publicity stunt. 4. She wasn't supposed to eat in her deposition and her gestures was pretty strange and funny at the same time. She obviously struggled to explain her lies. 5. This was from a premiere of never back down. Looked high. 

part 2. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nQzS5iZsA68

-----a personal note-----
I believe people should be forgiven for their mistakes...because we're only human right? BUT this Amber I'm talking about. She had done so many horrific things for so many years and got away with it. 
I only believe people should be forgiven if they hold themselves accountable, if they straight up apologised for their actions even if it's only once - But Amber never did and she's still out there continuing to destroy people's lives such as Johnny Depp, like Kate James etc by continuing to lie and play victim. This compilation is to show her true colours to the public which she hides with a mask
